text: Otak Creek is a stream in the U.S. state of Mississippi. Otak is a name derived from the Choctaw language purported to mean "beaver pond, lake". Variant names were "Otakoocha Creek", Otakooche Creek", and "Otokoochee Creek". ==References== Category:Rivers of Mississippi Category:Bodies of water of Jasper County, Mississippi
title: Otak Creek
